25_circuit_validation.py), [scripts/26_task_validation.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/scripts/26_task_validation.py), and [scripts/27_validation_ladder.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/scripts/27_validation_ladder.py); and circuit validation now derives a sensible default pathway readout instead of making `make circuit-validate` an unusable help entry, in [src/flywire_wave/validation_circuit.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/src/flywire_wave/validation_circuit.py). Docs and rationale were updated in [README.md](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/README.md), [docs/pipeline_notes.md](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/docs/pipeline_notes.md), and [docs/validation_ladder_notes/FW-M13-008_rationale.md](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/docs/validation_ladder_notes/FW-M13-008_rationale.md). Regression coverage was added in [tests/test_milestone13_readiness.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/tests/test_milestone13_readiness.py) and updated in [tests/test_validation_circuit.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/tests/test_validation_circuit.py).\n\nVerified:\n- `make test` passed: 194 tests\n- `make milestone13-readiness` passed: readiness status `ready`\n- packaged smoke inside readiness reported overall `review`, regression `pass`, with layer statuses `numerical=pass`, `morphology=pass`, `circuit=pass`, `task=review`\n- `python3 scripts/run_agent_tickets.py --tickets-file agent_tickets/milestone_13_validation_ladder_tickets.md --ticket-id FW-M13-008 --dry-run --runner true` passed\n\nThe readiness report records two explicit follow-ons, `FW-M13-FOLLOW-001` and `FW-M13-FOLLOW-002`, instead of leaving the remaining man